      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in a state of absolute preservation, reflecting a standard of care that exceeds the most rigorous expectations. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail mirrors its original showroom delivery condition. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands excellence without compromise, this offering represents the definitive choice in its class.",
